last-japanese-man-remaining-in-kazakhstan-a-kafkian-tale-of-the-plight-of-a-
japanese-pow-in-the-soviet-union/ "http://www.japansubculture.com/2011/02/the-
last-japanese-man-remaining-in-kazakhstan-a-kafkian-tale-of-the-plight-of-a-
japanese-pow-in-the-soviet-union/")。

